Humans process knowledge, simultaneously across multiple modes of data inputs. The way we learn, our experiences are all multimodal. We don‚Äôt have just vision, just audio and just text. In the previous examples we took in some text and generated some text. In this example you will use an image as the input and generate some text as the output. 

